import React from 'react'
import {CoursesWrapper, ModuleWrapper, ModuleGrid, Course1, Course2} from './CoursesElements'

const CourseList = () => {
    return (
        <CoursesWrapper>
            <ModuleWrapper>
                <ModuleGrid>
                    <Course1 />
                    <Course2 />
                </ModuleGrid>
            </ModuleWrapper>
        </CoursesWrapper>
    )
}

export default CourseList
